<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{وَنَزَعْنَا مَا فِي صُدُورِهِمْ مِنْ غل}</span> يَعْنِي: الْعَدَاوَةَ وَالْحَسَدَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{وَقَالُوا الْحَمْدُ لله الَّذِي هدَانَا لهَذَا}</span> يَعْنُونَ: الْإِيمَانَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{لَقَدْ جَاءَتْ رُسُلُ رَبنَا بِالْحَقِّ}</span> فِي الدُّنْيَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>سُورَة الْأَعْرَاف من الْآيَة <span class="c2">(٤٤)</span> إِلَى الْآيَة <span class="c2">(٤٧)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>